POST /users
Description: adds a new user. Takes username, email, and password

Request format:

{
    "user": {
        "username": "myoloye",
        "email": "myoloye@scu.edu",
        "password": "password"
    }
}

PUT /users/:id
Description: updates a user's about me

Request format:

{
    "about": "about me goes here"
}

GET /users/:id

Description: view a user profile

POST /recipe
Description: adds a new Recipe
